name: PROTONDictionary
0:
”Alexa, ask proton dictionary to tell me the definition of the word sympathy”
”Alexa, ask proton dictionary to tell me the synonyms of the word sympathy”
”Alexa, ask proton dictionary to tell me the antonyms of the word sympathy”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: proton dictionary
des:
The Proton Dictionary, can do a lot more than an ordinary dictionary. 
You can ask for 
Definitions, 
Synonyms, 
Antonyms, 
Examples, 
Domains (in which the particular word is most likely to be spoken), 
Etymology of the word, 
it's Spelling and last but not the least, 
you can also ask Alexa to Translate your word to some other languages also. 
This skill supports multiple languages too.
Here's a list of supported languages : 
English
Spanish
Malay
Swahili
Setswana
Northern Sotho
Latvian
Indonesian
Urdu
isiZulu
Romanian
Hindi
German
Portuguese
Tamil
Gujarati
This doesn't just stops here. If you ask again the skill will provide different results each time (given there are results to speak).
This skill is all you need to have.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
